Iranian Foreign Ministry Spokesperson Saeed Khatibzadeh said on Monday that Pakistani Foreign Minister Bilawal Bhutto Zardari would pay an official visit to Iran on Tuesday, adding that Turkmen President Serdar Berdimuhamedov would come to Iran with a detailed agenda as well as a visit by Armenian National Assembly Speaker Alen Simonyan this week. (Cover: Iranian Foreign Ministry Spokesperson Saeed Khatibzadeh holds a press conference in Tehran on May 9, 2022 /CFP)